OL,3,CFive arrested in Tameside as part of
OL,4,Clocal election fraud investigation
OL,6,FFive people have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of fraud offences relating
OL,8,Fto the recent local elections.
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police said four
OL,11,Fmen and a woman, aged between 23 and
OL,12,F47, were arrested on Thursday 21 May
OL,13,Ffollowing concerns around how
OL,14,Fcandidates were put forward for the
OL,15,Felection on 7 May in the St Peter's
OL,16,Fward in Tameside.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
