OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779437195
OL,3,CFive arrested in Tameside as part of
OL,4,Clocal election fraud investigation
OL,6,FThe investigation focuses on the
OL,7,Fprocess of selecting candidates and
OL,8,Fhow they were represented in the ward,
OL,9,Fas well as if the relevant legislation
OL,10,Fand electoral procedures were adhered
OL,11,Fto.
OL,13,FA spokesman said: "Following initial
OL,14,Finquiries last week, we have launched
OL,15,Fa full investigation into the
OL,16,Fallegations.
OL,18,F"Police are working with the Electoral
OL,19,FCommission and local partners," the
OL,20,Fspokesman said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
