OL,3,CFive arrested in Tameside as part of
OL,4,Clocal election fraud investigation
OL,6,FThe force said it had received the
OL,7,Freports about candidates in the days
OL,8,Fbefore and after the election. They
OL,9,Ffive remain in custody for questioning.
